      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t周育森，看来是这个：https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E5%91%A8%E8%82%B2%E6%A3%AE/3564287<br/>\n中共自己百度上的介绍：<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9EdWlDWDIwLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/DuiCX20.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/DuiCX20.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/DuiCX20.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\n显然是此人一旦把他于2019年底之前领导主持研究武汉病毒疫苗内容及过程透露于世，整个中国共产党政权刻意研究培育此病毒的罪恶阴谋将大白于世。于是中共国安杀了他，又不许任何公开记录媒体报道，甚至不说明54岁的周育森死于何处，何地点，何原因。就像潘汉年一样，知道内幕太多了，死，或用不许露面。这就是为中共土匪集团卖命的下场。研究Covid-19 疫苗需要Covid-19 病毒，而周于2020年2月24日提交了Covid19疫苗专利申请。<br/>\n<br/>\n但美国人显然不会放过即使已经被中共集团弄死的武汉病毒疫苗发起人。参议院的2023年4月报告明显指出周育森在研制Covid-19疫苗中的作用与日期。在武汉病毒被世界得知爆发前研制其疫苗，必须在其研制期间已经得到了病毒本身。<br/>\n<br/>\n周死时54岁，无已知疾病与健康问题。参看：<br/>\n<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/59558\" title=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/59558\">英泰晤士报 称 新冠爆发前武汉科学家与军方合造病毒</a>  <br/>\n<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/59940\" title=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/59940\">中国疫苗界多名高官专家壮年猝死被疑有黑幕</a><br/>\n<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/59944\" title=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/59944\">Covid19 泄漏于武汉病毒所的10个已知理由</a><br/>\n<a href=\"url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuZGFpbHltYWlsLmNvLnVrL25ld3MvYXJ0aWNsZS0xMjIwNTcwNS9DaGluZXNlLW1pbGl0YXJ5LWV4cGVydC1maWxlZC1wYXRlbnQtQ292aWQtdmFjY2luZS1kaWVkLW15c3RlcmlvdXMtY2lyY3Vtc3RhbmNlcy5odG1s\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-12205705/Chinese-military-expert-filed-patent-Covid-vaccine-died-mysterious-circumstances.html\">英国Daily Mail报：Chinese military expert who filed patent for Covid vaccine barely a month into country's first lockdown died in mysterious circumstances aged just 54</a><br/>\n<br/>\n<b>可是奇怪，网上有关论文罗列仍然有此人（周育森）迟至2022年的论文发表参与</b>：<br/>\n<a href=\"url/link/aHR0cDovL3d3dy5nbG9iYWxhdXRob3JpZC5jb20vV2ViUG9ydGFsL0F1dGhvclZpZXc_d2Q9R0FJRDEwMDAwNDA5JnJjPTI4MkUyQg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"http://www.globalauthorid.com/WebPortal/AuthorView?wd=GAID10000409&amp;rc=282E2B\">http://www.globalauthorid.com/WebPortal/AuthorView?wd=GAID10000409&amp;rc=282E2B</a><br/>\n包括其2020年7月参与发表的一篇“<a href=\"url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly9wZXNxdWlzYS5idnNhbHVkLm9yZy9nbG9iYWwtbGl0ZXJhdHVyZS1vbi1ub3ZlbC1jb3JvbmF2aXJ1cy0yMDE5LW5jb3YvcmVzb3VyY2UvcnUvY292aWR3aG8tMzc4MTMwP2xhbmc9emg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://pesquisa.bvsalud.org/global-literature-on-novel-coronavirus-2019-ncov/resource/ru/covidwho-378130?lang=zh\">A Mouse Model of SARS-CoV-2 Infection and Pathogenesis</a>” ？<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9WU1hRSEZhLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/VSXQHFa.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/VSXQHFa.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/VSXQHFa.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9hengzNHdQLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/azx34wP.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/azx34wP.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/azx34wP.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a> </div>",
